    "caption_text": "Zara presents Calma, an immersive installation offering a restful, sensorial experience at Palazzina Appiani. The space transforms into a peaceful escape from the city’s crowds, set within the serenity of Parco Sempione.\n \nThe project reinterprets the logic of ancient Roman thermae as a contemporary system of retreat, unfolding through a sequence of environments structured to settle perception. Created in partnership with Crosby Studios, it invites visitors to pause, reflect, and immerse themselves in a moment of calm.\n \nSalone del Mobile 2026 | April 21 — 26\nPalazzina Appiani, Viale Giorgio Byron 2, Milan\n \nBook your visit at zara.com/it\n \n#zara",
